               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; names of the kings; incipit of Text I; titles of the books to be read; titles and initial lines of the payers to be read; directives to the ministers; the abbreviation “yǝka” for “yǝbäl kahǝn” in fol. 41v; elements of the punctuation signs; Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 5r), a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
